      <title>苏格兰在“无法实现”的 2030 年气候变化目标上倒退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/scotland-retreats-on-out-of-reach-2030-climate-change-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏格兰政府放弃了到 2030 年将碳排放量减少 75% 的计划，承认该目标无法实现，需要重新调整应对气候变化的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/scotland-retreats-on-out-of-reach-2030-climate-change-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
